[b]Spawn Point Tool v1.2.0[/b]

[list]
[*]Added global respawn points for admins.
[*]Added a global placement hotkey.
[*]Added gold global markers and preview.
[*]Updated respawns so global points can be used for everyone.
[/list]

[b]Spawn Point Tool v1.1.0[/b]

[list]
[*]Improved the settings menu with clearer player, server, safety, cleanup, and about sections.
[*]Added quick links for the Workshop page, Steam profile, GitHub, and issue reports.
[*]Improved marker syncing and server setting updates.
[*]Cleaned up the addon structure for easier future updates.
[*]Improved respawn handling around blocked or unsafe points.
[/list]

[b]Spawn Point Tool v1.0.3[/b]

[list]
[*]Added player and server toggles for custom respawns.
[*]Added configurable marker sharing.
[*]Added optional blocked-spot checks when respawning.
[*]Added admin cleanup tools.
[*]Cleaned up the tool menu layout.
[*]Reduced the default danger check radius and cleaned up messages.
[/list]
